She leaned her head to look at Quickstrike.
"Well, we have that huge hole in the ceiling for those that can fly.  BUt 
your right, we don't have a back door.  When Scorponok gets back, we can 
drill a few passage ways in the back of the caverns and make a few escape 
routes.  Thanks for letting me know of this commander.  I hadn't thought of 
that.  I'll get on it as soon as Scorponok gets back."
